text: This survey will ask you about your health , medical conditions you may have had before or during pregnancy , tests or procedures you might have had done to you, and medical complications that may have occurred during and around the time of pregnancy. We will not share the answers with anyone, and it is important that you are as honest as possible.

Please try and give your best answer to each question. If there is a question you do not know or cannot remember the answer to, you may check "Don't Know". If you would prefer not to answer or if you do not want to answer, you can check "Refused".

For questions on "How often?" write in the number of times on average across specified time period(s), then choose the unit of time (per day, or per week, or per month). If the frequency was less than once per month, you check the box next to "less than once per month". For example, if you want to mark 3 times per week, you write in "3" on the blank line, and check the box next to week.
